### 3. 保留項目

> [!IMPORTANT]
> 以下不刪除：
> - [FindClosestPathNodeIndex()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#2013-2038) — 仍用於首次定位
> - [GetNodePriorities()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1730-1748) — MainForm 熱力圖可視化仍在用
> - [ActionCodeToKeys()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#481-506) — [SetPlannedPathWithActions](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#430-480) 仍在用
> - [MapLegacyAction()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1268-1282) / [ResolveSmartAction()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#888-937) — [BuildNavigationGraph](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#609-756) 仍在用
> - 壜落偵測邏輯（在 [UpdatePathState](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1835-1851) 中）— 已改為重新規劃

